entry.value: SELECT IIF(shp.IMO is null OR shp.IMO = 0, '', CONVERT(nvarchar,shp.IMO)) as imo, IIF(shp.CallSign is null, '', CONVERT(nvarchar, shp.CallSign)) as callsign, '${officialnumber}' as officialnumber, '${MMSI}' as mmsi, IIF(shp.Name is null, '', CONVERT(nvarchar, shp.Name)) as vesselName, Format(evt.TimeStmp, 'dd/MM/yy HH:mm:ss') as time, CASE WHEN evt.AlarmID = 485 THEN '0' WHEN evt.AlarmID = 486 THEN '1' WHEN evt.AlarmID = 487 THEN '2' WHEN evt.AlarmID = 488 THEN '3' END as visitStatusId, zon.ZoneName as zone FROM Events evt LEFT JOIN Zones zon on zon.ZoneID = evt.ZoneID LEFT JOIN ShipList shp on shp.MMSI = evt.MMSI WHERE EventID=${EventID}
